andard/pull/322\r\n* Update all non-major dependencies by @renovate-bot in https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/appengine-java-standard/pull/323\r\n* Add tests for error page mappings by @srinjoyray in https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/appengine-java-standard/pull/324\r\n* Issue #325 - fixes and testing for HttpServletRequest getServerName by @lachlan-roberts in https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/appengine-java-standard/pull/327\r\n* Issue #74 - remove trimmed servlets logic from Jetty12 EE8 & EE10 runtimes by @lachlan-roberts in https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/appengine-java-standard/pull/328\r\n* Update all non-major dependencies by @renovate-bot in https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/appengine-java-standard/pull/329\r\n* Update all non-major dependencies by @renovate-bot in https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/appengine-java-standard/pull/330\r\n* Update all non-major dependencies by @renovate-bot in https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/appengine-java-standard/pull/331\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/appengine-java-standard/compare/v2.0.31...v2.0.32",
